survey_response.review_text:
Dr Kamath is Extremely friendly and competent 
My son’s treatment was supposed to be two years however after one year came to halt after I got transferred from Noida to Mumbai in 2021. Dentist in Mumbai made it look like a big deal and complicated because of which we did not resume it. Unexpectedly we had to move to Bangalore in 6 months and Dr Kamath understood the case history in no time and clearly explained treatment course to complete. It’s been almost 10 months we are consulting and more than 100% satisfied… Treatment is expected to end in couple of months and we are extremely satisfied. Highly recommend !
Very professional and fair diagnosis, good clean clinic. Location is very convenient. On time appointment.

Dr Kamath is par excellence in guaging tooth problems correctly,advise the patient on the mode of treatment and executing the work to the patient’s full satisfaction.He is frank in telling a patient that he is erring against advices.
The doctor is always in a smiling mood and keeps the patient happy.
The doctor’s charges are very very moderate.
Doctor was very friendly and very less wait time. He listened to my queries very patiently and answered/explained everything in detail.

I went there for my wisdom teeth paining,.. Without x ray Dr Vikram told it should be removed.. I thought let believe doctor, went to extraction of teeth.. He gave Anastasia, immediately started to Extract, even not waited for 2 min. . It was immense pain I have ever experienced in my life.. I don't recommend this doctor... My legs always shivering whenever I passing by this clinic.
**** ******* *** ******  good behaviour and all my visits were awesome, comfortable and pocket friendly  😁
Doctor is friendly , treatment was very satisfied. Great advisor. Highly patient. Supports and guides me in education also.

review_reply.reply_text: Thank you very much. Happy to have been of help.

survey_response.review_text: Explains in detail and gives sufficient time to clear all doubts. Also educates upfront regarding post treatment issues if any and gives contact number for emergency consultation as well. Reasonable fees as well.

** ******** ** **** * clinic clean and hygienic
Dr assistant approach also nice hope same should be maintained
Very friendly person and explains the problem very well n doesn’t makes it feel complex, his clinic is very well maintained and hygienic.
